        "jsonBody": "={{\n  {\n    \"model\": \"llama-3.3-70b-versatile\",\n    \"messages\": [\n      {\n        \"role\": \"user\",\n        \"content\": `Create a professional LinkedIn marketing post about our recent outreach.\n\nDETAILS:\n- Company we contacted: ${$('Code in JavaScript2').item.json.companyName}\n- Their Industry: ${$('Code in JavaScript2').item.json.industry}\n- Location: ${$('Code in JavaScript2').item.json.city}\n- Our Service: Elite DevOps & AI Automation\n\nREQUIREMENTS:\n1. Hook: Start with an interesting fact or question about the ${$('Code in JavaScript2').item.json.industry} industry.\n2. Value: Briefly mention how automation helps companies in ${$('Code in JavaScript2').item.json.city} scale.\n3. Call to Action: Ask a question to encourage comments.\n4. Length: Short (under 100 words).\n5. Hashtags: Include #${$('Code in JavaScript2').item.json.industry.replace(/\\s+/g, '')}Tech and #AIAutomation.\n6. Style: Professional but engaging. No emojis.`\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}}",
        "options": {}
